@base = http://localhost:5182

##########  Auth (dev)  ##########

### 1. Get a dev JWT — SEND THIS ONE FIRST (requests below read its response)
# @name devtoken
GET {{base}}/dev/token

### 2. Secured POST WITHOUT a token  ->  401 Unauthorized
POST {{base}}/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{ "name": "NoAuth", "price": 10, "categoryId": 1 }

### 3. Secured POST WITH the token  ->  201 Created  (run #1 first!)
POST {{base}}/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{devtoken.response.body.$.access_token}}

{ "name": "AuthedWebcam", "price": 40, "categoryId": 1 }

### 4. Get an ADMIN dev JWT (adds role=admin) — SEND before the admin DELETE below
# @name admintoken
GET {{base}}/dev/token?admin=true

### 5. DELETE with the NON-admin token  ->  403 Forbidden (authenticated, but not an admin)
DELETE {{base}}/v1/products/3
Authorization: Bearer {{devtoken.response.body.$.access_token}}

### 6. DELETE with the ADMIN token  ->  204 No Content  (run #4 first!)
DELETE {{base}}/v1/products/3
Authorization: Bearer {{admintoken.response.body.$.access_token}}

##########  API v1  ##########

### v1 - List all products (200)
GET {{base}}/v1/products

### v1 - Get one product (200)
GET {{base}}/v1/products/1

### v1 - Get a missing product (404)
GET {{base}}/v1/products/999

### v1 - Create a product (201 Created + Location header)
POST {{base}}/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Headset",
  "price": 59.99,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### v1 - Create with a NON-EXISTENT category (400 ProblemDetails)
POST {{base}}/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Headset",
  "price": 59.99,
  "categoryId": 999
}

### v1 - Create an INVALID product (400 ProblemDetails from the filter)
POST {{base}}/v1/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "price": -5,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### v1 - Update a product (204 No Content)
PUT {{base}}/v1/products/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Keyboard Pro",
  "price": 39.99,
  "categoryId": 1
}

### v1 - Delete a product (needs admin token; 204, then 404 on re-run)
DELETE {{base}}/v1/products/2
Authorization: Bearer {{admintoken.response.body.$.access_token}}

##########  API v2 (adds DisplayPrice)  ##########

### v2 - List all products (200) - note the extra "DisplayPrice" field
GET {{base}}/v2/products

##########  Relationships  ##########

### Product with its category name (navigates Product -> Category)
GET {{base}}/v1/products/1/with-category

### Categories with product counts (reverse navigation Category -> Products)
GET {{base}}/v1/categories

##########  Pagination  ##########

### Page 1, 2 per page (Skip/Take -> SQL OFFSET/LIMIT) - watch the console for the SQL
GET {{base}}/v1/products/page?page=1&size=2

### Page 2, 2 per page
GET {{base}}/v1/products/page?page=2&size=2
